&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a high-impact Finance &amp;amp; Accounting Manager to join our growing Finance team. In this role, you will serve as a key contributor to financial planning, forecasting, and reporting across the organization. You will report directly to the Director of Finance and support the financial direction of a fast-growing healthcare technology company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a member of a lean, high-performing finance team, you will have broad exposure across the business — from partnering with leadership on strategic financial decisions to supporting the accounting team with month-end close, variance analysis, and reporting. This is not a siloed role; you will work cross-functionally across the organization to provide the financial insight that drives business decisions. If you thrive in a dynamic environment where you can build processes, solve novel problems, and see the direct impact of your work, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties/Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the preparation of monthly, quarterly, and annual financial reporting packages, including P&amp;amp;L, balance sheet, and cash flow analysis, with variance commentary comparing actuals to budget and prior periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the annual budgeting and forecasting process, including gathering inputs from department heads, consolidating financial plans, and maintaining rolling forecasts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain financial models to support scenario analysis, strategic planning, and investor or board-level reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Accounting team on month-end close activities, ensuring alignment between operational results and GAAP financial statements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support financial audits, tax preparation, and compliance reporting, serving as a key point of contact for information requests and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in maintaining the integrity of the general ledger by reviewing account reconciliations and supporting journal entry preparation as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the preparation of Board of Directors and executive-level presentations, translating financial data into clear narratives and actionable insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track, maintain, and report on key performance indicators (KPIs) and metrics, ensuring leadership has timely and accurate visibility into business performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
